OL,3,CArmy double agent operations within
OL,4,CIRA cost lives, report finds
OL,6,FKenova has probed the activities of
OL,7,Fthe agent Stakeknife within the
OL,8,FProvisional IRA. He has not been
OL,9,Fidentified in the report, however, the
OL,10,Freport authors have called on the
OL,11,Fgovernment to reveal his identity and
OL,12,Fexpect it to do so in order that it be
OL,13,Fincluded in the final Kenova report.
OL,15,FInvestigators examined 101 killings
OL,16,Fand abductions linked to the IRA unit
OL,17,Fresponsible for interrogating and
OL,18,Ftorturing people suspected of passing
OL,19,Finformation to the security forces
OL,20,Fduring the conflict.
