OL,6,FStakeknife was part of the terror
OL,7,Fgroup's internal security unit - known
OL,8,Fas the 'nutting squad'. and Kenova
OL,9,Fexamined crimes such as murder and
OL,10,Ftorture, and the role played by the
OL,11,Fsecurity services, including MI5.
OL,13,FThe Kenova investigation was
OL,14,Foriginally headed up by Jon Boutcher
OL,15,Fbut he left the position to take up
OL,16,Fthe role of chief constable of the
OL,17,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland.
