OL,6,FLast week the Public Prosecution
OL,7,FService in Northern Ireland announced
OL,8,Fthat no prosecutions would be pursued
OL,9,Fafter consideration of the last batch
OL,10,Fof files from the investigation.
OL,12,FSome 32 people, including former
OL,13,Fpolice, former military personnel and
OL,14,Fpeople linked with the IRA, were
OL,15,Fconsidered for prosecution on a range
OL,16,Fof charges from murder and abduction
OL,17,Fto misconduct in public office and
OL,18,Fperjury.
OL,20,FHowever, the PPS found there was
OL,21,Finsufficient evidence to pursue cases.
