OL,11,Fhad passed "strong evidence of very
OL,12,Fserious criminality" by Scappaticci to
OL,13,Fprosecutors in Northern Ireland prior
OL,14,Fto his death.
OL,16,FThe report also dismisses rumours that
OL,17,FScappaticci might still be alive.
