OL,6,FThe report also calls on the UK and
OL,7,Fthe IRA to apologies to bereaved
OL,8,Ffamilies and victims of the ISU, the
OL,9,Fsecurity forces for failings amid a
OL,10,F"maverick" culture for handling agents
OL,11,Fand intelligence; and the IRA for the
