OL,6,F"Furthermore, there were undoubtedly
OL,7,Foccasions when Stakeknife ignored his
OL,8,Fhandlers, acted outside his tasking
OL,9,Fand did things he should not have done
OL,10,Fand when very serious risks were run."
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Chris
OL,13,FHeaton-Harris, said: "There can be no
OL,14,Fdoubt that the way Operation Kenova
OL,15,Fhas conducted its work since being
OL,16,Fcommissioned in 2016 has gained the
OL,17,Ftrust of many families who have long
OL,18,Fbeen seeking answers as to what
OL,19,Fexactly happened when their loved ones
OL,20,Fwere so brutally murdered by, and on
OL,21,Fthe orders of, the Provisional IRA.
