OL,4,CIRA cost lives, report finds
OL,6,F"Over 3,500 people from all parts of
OL,7,Fthe community were killed during the
OL,8,FTroubles and tens of thousands more
OL,9,Finjured. Over 1,000 of those killed
OL,10,Fwere members of the security forces.
OL,11,FTheir bravery, courage, dedication and
OL,12,Fsacrifice in seeking to uphold
OL,13,Fdemocracy and the rule of law must
OL,14,Fnever be forgotten.
OL,16,FWe must remember too that the vast
OL,17,Fmajority of deaths during the
OL,18,FTroubles, around 90%, were perpetrated
OL,19,Fby terrorist organisations - in the
OL,20,Fsubstance of this report, by the
OL,21,FProvisional IRA.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                         G16/19
