OL,9,Fof the report. It contains several
OL,10,Fspecific, very serious allegations
OL,11,Fthat remain subject to consideration
OL,12,Fby the courts.
OL,14,F"It would not be right for the
OL,15,Fgovernment to make any comment on the
OL,16,Fsubstance of the Interim Report until
OL,17,Fthe conclusion of litigation related
OL,18,Fto it.
